categories: Category:Articles that are known by a nickname

nodes.text: "Blackout" was the nickname of a human test pilot for the First Order's TIE/vn space superiority fighters during the war against the Resistance. At some point, Blackout was stationed on a world with bodies of water and volcanic areas, proceeding to skim the water's surface while firing the craft's laser cannons. At this time, they were considered ill-fated.
